reviews.text: I love eating at The Spaghetti House just because their selection of foods really match my taste palette. Their Causeway Bay branch is well-designed with friendly staff and quickly service. Upon arrival, I was promptly seated and my food was delivered very soon after I placed an order. I had a lovely lunch here, and thanks for the great service all-around!
Meal with a friend, convenient spot with plenty of seats. Wide range of food, as their name, spaghetti is tasty as it should be. Love their avocado salad. Nice restaurant for lunch or dinner.
Love their pasta n pizza menu..very flavorful...highly recommend
Fast service and delicious food
